  <title translate="true">Y-Units-Counts</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Y-Axis:<keyword translate="true">Units at Start</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para><table styleclass="MotionPupup" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Counts</text><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">refer to encoder counts of a Servo Control system, or to &apos;Steps&apos; of a Stepper-Motor system. The user can set the motion plot in counts, both along the X–axis and the Y–axis.</text></para>
          <para><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">It is convenient to set the units to counts when the motion data is to be directly downloaded to a motor system that will accept the data as a series of integer numbers.</text></para>
          <para><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">If you wish to save the motion data in counts using the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Tools-DataTransfer" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#800000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Data-Transfer</link><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> dialog-box, then you should make sure the data is as follows:</text></para>
          <para style="margin-left:31px;"><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">1. Set the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-X-Units" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#800000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">X–axis units</link><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> and the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Y-Units" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#800000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Y–axis position units</link><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> to counts.</text></para>
          <para style="text-indent:-16px; margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">2. Make sure the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Edit-Active-Motion-Settings" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#800000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">number-of-steps</link><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> is the same as the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Edit-Active-Motion-Settings" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#800000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Counts per Cycle</link><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> and that this is the same as the number of counts per cycle of the Pacer encoder. </text></para>
          <para style="text-indent:-11px; margin-left:41px;"><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">3. Set the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Edit-Active-Motion-Settings" anchor="DataFormat" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#800000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">Decimal Places</link><text styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> to zero.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
